Gabriela Sabatini's winless agony continued on  Sunday as she squandered a set lead to gift Mary Joe Fernandez victory in the  final of the Strasbourg tournament.
The Argentinian has not won a tournament since the 1992 Italian Open.
For Fernandez, the 4-6, 6-4, 6-0 victory was a major boost as she prepares  for this week's French Open.
Her comeback will also have brought back memories of her stirring rally  against Sabatini in last year's Roland Garros quarter finals, when she  recovered a set and 5-1 deficit to beat the Argentinian.
Mary Joe Fernandez (USA x3) bt Gabriela Sabatini (Argentina x1) 4-6, 6-4,  6-0
